Speech to Text: Hi doctor, I fell down and I got hurt in my forehead. Can you please tell me what it is?
Doctor's Response: With what I see, I think you have a laceration on your forehead, it appears to be a clean cut, likely from a sharp object. You may need some wound care to prevent infection and promote healing, I would suggest keeping the area clean with mild soap and water, applying an antibiotic ointment, and covering it with a bandage, also you may want to consider taking over-the-counter pain relievers if you're experiencing discomfort.
